<HEAD>

<TITLE> Subscribe to The Atlantic Monthly </TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="ffffff">

<center> <img src="../images/logosmal.gif"> </center>

<center><H2> Atlantic Monthly Subscriptions </H2></center>

<P>

Every month <b>The Atlantic Monthly </b> places you at the leading edge of contemporary issues. Plus the very best in fiction, travel, food and humor. <P>

Voted "most insightful and thought-provoking magazine" by readers of the
American Journalism Review, called a "must-read" by judges for the National
Magazine Awards, <b>The Atlantic</b> explores the issues that Americans aren't just
talking about, but <i>living</i>. <p>

Read <b>The Atlantic</b> in print -- at home or on the go. It's well-designed for easy 
reading and beautifully illustrated. There's no meter running, so take your
time with our in-depth articles. Subscribe today! <p>

<P>
<A HREF="http://www.theatlantic.com/atlantic/xchg/circ/twoyear.htm"><B>Two-year subscription</B></A><BR>$24 -- One dollar an issue. Best deal! 
</P>
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.theatlantic.com/atlantic/xchg/circ/oneyear.htm"><B>One-year subscription </B></A><BR>$14.95 -- Save 58% off the cover price 
</P>
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.theatlantic.com/atlantic/xchg/circ/gift.htm"><B>Gift subscription </B></A><BR>$14.95 -- Free gift card 
</P>

<FONT SIZE="-1">Single-copy price: $2.95 per issue.</FONT>

<P>

</P>


<BR>


<font size=1>


Copyright &copy; 1996 by The Atlantic Monthly Company.  All rights reserved.


</font>

