<title>
About The Atlantic
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=ffffff><p>

<p>
<a name="top">	<!--REFERENCE POINT; TOP OF PAGE-->
<center>
			<!--HEADER GRAPHIC-->
			
<a href="../images/headbar.map"> <img src="../images/headbar.gif" ISMAP 
width=480 height=100 BORDER=0 alt="The Atlantic Monthly"></a>

</center>
<p>



<center>
<h2>About <I>The Atlantic Monthly</I></h2>
</center>
<p>
<br>

<blockquote>
<font size=4><i>The Atlantic Monthly</i>, founded in 1857, is a general-interest magazine covering
a broad range of topics. Our contributors have ranged from Walt Whitman to
Martin Luther King, Jr., from Emily Dickinson to John F. Kennedy, from Mark Twain to
Teller (of Penn &amp; Teller), from Bertrand Russell to Eleanor Roosevelt, from
John Kenneth Galbraith to John Updike.<p>


<ul>

<li>The <A HREF="./people/staff.htm">New Media Staff,</A> and 
their mini-bios 
	
<li>The magazine <a href="masthead.htm">Masthead</a>, with biographies of the editors
	
<li><a href="Atlhistf.htm">A History of <i>The Atlantic</i></a> (by Cullen Murphy, managing editor)
	
<li>FAQs and <a href="atlfaqf.htm">Facts About <i>The Atlantic Monthly</i></a>
	
<li>About How to Resolve <a href="atlsubf.htm">Subscription Problems</a>
	
<li>About <i>The Atlantic</i>'s <a href="./intern.htm">career and 
	internship opportunities</a>
	

</ul><p>
</blockquote>

<p><hr>
</font>
<font size=1>
Copyright &copy; 1995 The Atlantic Monthly.  All rights reserved.
</font>
<p>

