<hr><H2> <B> Welcome to The Atlantic Monthly Store! </H2> </B><br>




</center>



Thank you for stopping by our store.  Click on any of the selections below to see



a picture of the item and a detailed description. Most of our books are offered 



at 25 percent off the cover price. Shipping is free for   all  purchases. If 

you'd like more detailed information on the store, please 

read our  <A  HREF="about.htm">about the store</A> page. Direct any 



questions  or comments to <A HREF="mailto:tony@the atlantic.com">tony@theatlantic.com</A>.

<pre>



</pre>

