</P>

<P>
	Under no circumstances shall The Atlantic Monthly Company or any of its officers, directors, employees, subsidiaries, agents, parents, or affiliates be held liable for any damages, whether incidental, indirect, special or consequential damages and including without limitation, lost revenues or lost profits arising from or in connection with the use or performance of the information on this server or the Internet generally.
