<center>
<blockquote>
<font size=2>
Welcome to <I>The Atlantic Monthly</I>'s Poetry Pages, a multimedia 
feature devoted to poets and poetry, both classic and contemporary.  This 
area is updated regularly, with new readings by poets featured in each 
issue of the magazine, as well as poetry and essays from <I>The Atlantic</I>'s 
archive.<p> </font>
