<DOCHDR>
http://www.theatlantic.com:80/atlantic/election/connection/crime/windows.htm 205.216.101.132 19970117193147 text/html 45433
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0a
Date: Fri, 17 Jan 1997 19:31:40 GMT
