<BLOCKQUOTE>
Have you seen a great 
quote you'd like to share?  Send it to us and it may become the next "For 
the Record." Please limit submissions to a hundred words or less and be 
sure to include very specific source information (see below).  We'll credit 
you for your find.
</BLOCKQUOTE>

