<DOCHDR>
http://www.theatlantic.com:80/atlantic/issues/96mar/everyman/everyman.htm 205.216.101.132 19970117174310 text/html 23070
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0a
Date: Fri, 17 Jan 1997 17:43:07 GMT
